<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #0d1117;
      color: #c9d1d9;
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    
    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #21262d;
    }
    h1 { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: #58a6ff; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .subtitle { font-size: 18px; color: #8b949e; }
    .nav-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 16px;
      color: #8b949e;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .nav-link:hover { color: #58a6ff; }
    
    .plans {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    
    .plan-card {
      background: #161b22;
      border: 2px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 32px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      position: relative;
    }
    .plan-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      border-color: #58a6ff;
    }
    .plan-card.popular {
      border-color: #238636;
      background: #0d1b0f;
    }
    .plan-card.popular::before {
      content: '‚≠ê MOST POPULAR';
      position: absolute;
      top: -12px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: #238636;
      color: white;
      padding: 4px 16px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .plan-card.current {
      border-color: #1f6feb;
    }
    
    .plan-name {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #c9d1d9;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .plan-price {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #58a6ff;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .plan-price small {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #8b949e;
    }
    .plan-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #8b949e;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      min-height: 40px;
    }
    
    .plan-features {
      list-style: none;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .plan-features li {
      padding: 8px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #c9d1d9;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .plan-features li::before {
      content: '‚úì';
      color: #238636;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: block;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: #238636;
      color: white;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #2ea043; }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: #21262d;
      color: #c9d1d9;
      border: 1px solid #30363d;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: #30363d; }
    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: #58a6ff;
      border: 1px solid #58a6ff;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
      background: #58a6ff;
      color: #0d1117;
    }
    .btn:disabled {
      opacity: 0.5;
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }
    
    .faq {
      background: #161b22;
      border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 32px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .faq h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #c9d1d9;
    }
    .faq-item {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .faq-question {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #c9d1d9;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .faq-answer {
      color: #8b949e;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .current-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      background: #1f6feb;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>üíé Choose Your Plan</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Select the plan that works best for your team</p>
      <a href="/" class="nav-link">‚Üê Back to Dashboard</a>
    </header>

    <div class="plans">
      <!-- Free Plan -->
      <div class="plan-card <%= user.subscriptionTier === 'free' ? 'current' : '' %>">
        <div class="plan-name">
          Free
          <% if (user.subscriptionTier === 'free') { %>
            <span class="current-badge">CURRENT</span>
          <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="plan-price">
          $0
          <small>/month</small>
        </div>
        <div class="plan-desc">Perfect for trying out Peer</div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>1,000 AI tokens</li>
          <li>Unlimited repositories</li>
          <li>Basic code analysis</li>
          <li>Community support</li>
        </ul>
        <% if (user.subscriptionTier === 'free') { %>
          <button class="btn btn-secondary" disabled>Current Plan</button>
        <% } else { %>
          <form action="/settings/subscription/downgrade" method="POST">
            <button class="btn btn-outline" type="submit">Downgrade</button>
          </form>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <!-- Pro Plan -->
      <div class="plan-card popular <%= user.subscriptionTier === 'pro' ? 'current' : '' %>">
        <div class="plan-name">
          Pro
          <% if (user.subscriptionTier === 'pro') { %>
            <span class="current-badge">CURRENT</span>
          <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="plan-price">
          $29
          <small>/month</small>
        </div>
        <div class="plan-desc">For professional developers</div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>100,000 AI tokens/month</li>
          <li>Unlimited repositories</li>
          <li>Advanced code analysis</li>
          <li>Priority support</li>
          <li>Auto-merge capabilities</li>
          <li>Custom rules</li>
        </ul>
        <% if (user.subscriptionTier === 'pro') { %>
          <button class="btn btn-secondary" disabled>Current Plan</button>
        <% } else { %>
          <form action="/settings/subscription/checkout" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="plan" value="pro" />
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Upgrade to Pro</button>
          </form>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <!-- Enterprise Plan -->
      <div class="plan-card <%= user.subscriptionTier === 'enterprise' ? 'current' : '' %>">
        <div class="plan-name">
          Enterprise
          <% if (user.subscriptionTier === 'enterprise') { %>
            <span class="current-badge">CURRENT</span>
          <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="plan-price">
          $99
          <small>/month</small>
        </div>
        <div class="plan-desc">For teams and organizations</div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>Unlimited AI tokens</li>
          <li>Unlimited repositories</li>
          <li>Advanced code analysis</li>
          <li>24/7 dedicated support</li>
          <li>Auto-merge capabilities</li>
          <li>Custom rules & workflows</li>
          <li>SSO & team management</li>
          <li>SLA guarantee</li>
        </ul>
        <% if (user.subscriptionTier === 'enterprise') { %>
          <button class="btn btn-secondary" disabled>Current Plan</button>
        <% } else { %>
          <form action="/settings/subscription/checkout" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="plan" value="enterprise" />
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Upgrade to Enterprise</button>
          </form>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h2>‚ùì Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">What are AI tokens?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          Tokens are units of text that AI models process. Roughly, 1 token ‚âà 4 characters. 
          Analyzing a typical PR uses 500-2000 tokens.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Can I use my own API keys?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          Yes! Go to <a href="/settings/api-keys" style="color: #58a6ff;">API Keys</a> to add your own Groq or Gemini keys. 
          This lets you use your own credits instead of ours.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Can I cancel anytime?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          Yes, you can cancel your subscription at any time. You'll keep access until the end of your billing period.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">Is payment secure?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          We use industry-standard encryption and never store your payment details directly.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
